    "story_name": "不为人知的真相 第19章 3-3 自白",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "芬罗达道出他为了监视王子，\\n亲手操纵纳姆的记忆以及与王子的相遇。\\n不仅如此，他还告知众人王子\\n是用魔神肉体的碎片在精灵秘术下\\n诞生的生命。众人顿时哑口无言。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "你……\\n本不该在南格拉斯迪亚，\\n而是该在这个精灵国生活的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "生活在这个你出生的故乡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "等、等一下！\\n这里……是我的故乡？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么可能……\\n纳姆应该是在南格拉斯迪亚\\n出生的才对……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "对、对啊！\\n因为我从来都没走出过\\n南格拉斯迪亚啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "你之所以不记得\\n关于这个国家的任何事，\\n都怪我。是我——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "把你在精灵国生活过的记忆\\n全部封印、篡改了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你说……把记忆封印了……\\n这种事真的做得到吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "我们精灵族自古以来\\n就发明了各种各样的秘术。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "其中……有一种秘术\\n可以操纵生者的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "在雪山的时候，我把如何来到\\n这栋宅邸的路线告诉纳姆\\n也是运用了这个秘术的一部分。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "我用秘术封印了你的记忆，\\n再赋予你在南格拉斯迪亚\\n长大的虚假记忆……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "此外，我还让你陷入沉睡，\\n命人把你带去南格拉斯迪亚……\\n然后——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "让你在索尔·阿尔贝里亚的\\n王宫醒来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "等一下！\\n难道纳姆与我和塞西娅\\n相遇也是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "我认为你们以这样的形式\\n相遇比较好，才策划了这一切……\\n为了假装成自然的相遇……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "那天，我和塞西娅的相遇\\n原来……不是偶然吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "我还遇到了尤蒂尔，\\n之后我们三个\\n变得越来越要好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "这一切，全都，怎么会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "对不起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我可以提一个问题吗？\\n就算你说的这些都是真的，\\n我也不懂你为什么要这么做……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "假设你真的将纳姆从精灵国\\n带了出来，让她在王宫醒来，\\n又是出于什么目的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊……你为什么\\n非要这么做呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "因为我需要通过纳姆\\n来监视尤蒂尔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你要通过纳姆……\\n监视尤蒂尔？\\n到底是怎么一回事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "你这家伙别说些\\n不明所以的话，\\n好好把话讲清楚啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "纳姆她……她的魔力在我们\\n精灵族当中也是非常优秀的。\\n于是我利用了她的魔力……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "我用魔力让你的记忆\\n和知觉能够直接\\n传达到我这里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "这样我即使身在精灵国，\\n也能够随时掌握\\n尤蒂尔的动向……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "！？\\n那、那么，我……\\n至今为止的所见所闻都……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "所有的一切都\\n传达到了你这里，是吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "正是如此……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "……\\n怎么会，怎么会这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "芬罗达……\\n你竟然做出这种事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "开什么玩笑啊！\\n你把纳姆当成什么了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "把纳姆当成工具一样对待，\\n你以为你是谁啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "这一切都是我的错……\\n我不会推脱罪责……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你现在道歉还有什么用！\\n都已经把纳姆的人生\\n弄得一团糟了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "这种行为绝对无法原谅！\\n你怎么忍心做出\\n这等残酷的事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "先冷静一下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "谢斯大人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "他正打算说出自己\\n为什么会做这种事呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01",
                "100003_01",
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "芬罗达，\\n请你为我们解答吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你不惜那么做也要“监视”\\n尤蒂尔的理由……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "还有这件事与你和父王定下密约，\\n将奈迪犹和尤蒂尔\\n调换有什么联系。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢斯姐姐……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "说出真相吧。\\n你有义务回答这些。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "我需要一直监视\\n尤蒂尔，以防他的身体\\n出现异常情况……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "亲爱的他的身体怎么了？\\n你快给我说清楚！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "芬罗达，告诉我吧！\\n我的身体，到底怎么了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "尤蒂尔……\\n你——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "你的生命\\n并不是自然诞生的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "而是通过精灵的秘术，\\n由我以“异界者”为基础，\\n创造出来的生命……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……\\n我、我是……\\n通过精灵的……秘术……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "而且，你这具躯体的根基……\\n就是在曾经的战争中\\n飞散到世界各地的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "魔神肉体的碎片……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07",
                "100010_05",
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_06_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}